to return with Na-ri back then.

272
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:28,606
Se-ah. Don't think like that.

273
00:35:30,608 --> 00:35:32,235
You tried your best.

274
00:35:49,293 --> 00:35:52,964
GIRIGO
WOULD YOU LIKE TO DELETE THIS APP?

275
00:35:53,673 --> 00:35:54,757
GIRIGO HAS BEEN DELETED

276
00:36:02,390 --> 00:36:03,849
Let's say this is the car.

277
00:36:04,767 --> 00:36:08,354
It pierced right through me here,
even through the car door.

278
00:36:08,437 --> 00:36:11,774
But it pinned me at this height
where I couldn't stand or sit,

279
00:36:11,857 --> 00:36:13,943
and the blood started gushing out.

280
00:36:14,026 --> 00:36:16,153
Well, it went right through me like this.

281
00:36:16,237 --> 00:36:19,865
So I thought I was really going to die.

282
00:36:19,949 --> 00:36:22,118
At that moment, I started fading out.

283
00:36:22,201 --> 00:36:27,290
I was crossing the river to the afterlife
with the Grim Reaper, arm-in-arm.

284
00:36:27,373 --> 00:36:31,210
I almost made it across,
but I heard this voice behind me.

285
00:36:31,294 --> 00:36:33,838
"Brother-in-law!"

286
00:36:33,921 --> 00:36:37,842
My brother-in-law on the other side
was crying his eyes out.

287
00:36:37,925 --> 00:36:39,385
What? I swear I didn't cry!

288
00:36:41,554 --> 00:36:42,596
God, what do we do?

289
00:36:42,680 --> 00:36:44,640
You so did cry. He cried, didn't he?

290
00:36:44,724 --> 00:36:46,267
Seriously.

291
00:36:48,311 --> 00:36:51,480
At that moment, the first thing
that came to mind was Haetsal's face.

292
00:36:59,447 --> 00:37:01,198
By the way, I saw it again.

293
00:37:01,741 --> 00:37:03,909
When you helped Hyeong-wook move on,

294
00:37:03,993 --> 00:37:05,786
I could see him.

295
00:37:08,831 --> 00:37:10,249
But that's not all.

296
00:37:10,750 --> 00:37:16,172
I can see the power that dwells in you
and even how it moves.

297
00:37:19,300 --> 00:37:20,134
What?

298
00:37:20,217 --> 00:37:25,306
Are you talking about what you told me
at the hospital, brother-in-law?

299
00:37:25,389 --> 00:37:26,349
Yeah.

300
00:37:28,684 --> 00:37:29,643
Haetsal.

301
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,190
Well…

302
00:37:37,568 --> 00:37:39,487
I think I've found a way.

303
00:37:42,073 --> 00:37:44,658
A way for you to get out of this house.

304
00:37:45,910 --> 00:37:46,744
Yeah.

305
00:39:42,234 --> 00:39:44,778
050201
WHY DO YOU THINK CHOI HYEONG-WOOK DIED?

306
00:39:56,665 --> 00:39:59,627
WELL… I'LL TELL YOU
ONCE YOU BRING ME THE PHONE. LOL

307
00:39:59,710 --> 00:40:00,669
DID YOU FIND IT?

308
00:40:00,753 --> 00:40:02,963
I FOUND IT! IT REALLY WAS STILL THERE!

309
00:40:05,174 --> 00:40:07,468
050201 IS TYPING…

310
00:40:07,551 --> 00:40:09,386
SEE? WHAT DID I TELL YOU? LOL

311
00:40:17,144 --> 00:40:19,522
GIRIGO

312
00:43:58,741 --> 00:44:01,493
Subtitle translation by: Sung In Jang
